      • newAsync

        public static void newAsync(@NonNull
                            android.content.Context context)
        Create a new empty cart. This method is Asynchronous. The result is broadcast on New#BROADCAST_ACTION the broadcast contains the status whether cart creation was Successful or not If Successful the bundle contains CartId.
        Parameters:
        context - required to make a call to the web server

      • newSync

      • orderAsync

        public static void orderAsync(@NonNull
                              android.content.Context context,
                              @NonNull
                              java.lang.String cartId)
        Create an order from a cart. This will lock the cart. And any subsequent action on the cart itself is impossible. This method is Asynchronous. The result is broadcast on Order#BROADCAST_ACTION the broadcast contains the status whether order creation was Successful or not If Successful the bundle contains OrderId.
        Parameters:
        context - required to make a call to the web server
        cartId - the id of the cart to be converted to order
